2026-05-15T05:16:46.9333303Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9333668Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9333856Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9334194Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9334508Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9334837Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9335146Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9335486Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T05:16:46.9335810Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
